{
  "stem": "5371.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And somebody must have said something to somebody, and I was called out by the-- it's called the 'political abteilung.' It was the political section of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the evening, after roll call, my number was called out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I really didn't know why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I already got scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was called in to that political section of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they start asking me, who gave me the money and who did I give the money to?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I already heard so many stories about what's going on in camp, so I figured, you know, I'm not going to involve anybody else anymore, that, you know, this is going to be my end, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I resigned to the idea that that's it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I wouldn't involve.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- I got beat-- they were beating me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were hanging me on-- [CRYING] [DRINKS] They were hanging me by my hands, in the back, for about a half an hour, for 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they were kicking me with bayonets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, I have a big mark, here, [INAUDIBLE] stomach.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And after a few weeks, they let me go and I went back to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my kapo told me that I have a death sentence, that whenever they're going to call me, in the evening, after roll call, that I am transferred to Block 11A.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I knew that I'm being shot there, because there was a black wall there, he told me, and they put you up against the black wall and they shoot you.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This lasted like six months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But after six months, the head of the camp, of the Auschwitz camp, was, naturally, a German, and he was number one.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
